        <li>Digital transformation guidance</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        The specific scope, deliverables, and timeline for services will be outlined in individual client agreements.
      </p>

      <h2>Payments and Refund Policy</h2>
      <h3>Payment Terms</h3>
